-- Gazprom Board Recommends 2012 Dividend of 5.99 Rubles a Share
-- B y   J a k e   R u d n i t s k y
-- 2013-05-21T09:00:07Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-05-21/gazprom-board-recommends-2012-dividend-of-5-99-rubles-a-share.html
OAO Gazprom’s board recommended a
2012 dividend of 5.99 rubles a share, in line with a proposal in
April by the company’s management,  Russia ’s state natural-gas
exporter said today in an e-mailed statement.  The payout is less than the prior year’s 8.97 rubles after
net income fell 37 percent under Russian Accounting Standards.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jake Rudnitsky in Moscow at 
